== English ==

=== Noun ===
#rushed action. When one is "in a hurry" (adverbial phrase) it means one is doing things quickly and often impatiently.

=== Verb ===
#To do things quickly. (e.g. ''He's hurrying because he's late.'')
#To speed up the rate of doing something. (e.g. ''If you don't hurry you wont finish on time.)

